{"tid":554934,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"婆婆推車仔 行紅隧過海去九龍","createTime":"2018-02-09T03:41:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-09T18:22:48.000Z","uid":39464,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"6ea5be5a2c3b0698fae5b914915bd2668508ba0b","tid":554934,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T03:41:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180209/large/1518146422_94f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180209%2Flarge%2F1518146422_94f2.jpg&h=c1695e4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早上10時11分，紅磡海底隧道的職員，發現一名老婦推着手推車進入管道往九龍方向前行，連忙報警。警員接報到場，在九龍出口截獲老婦，她的手推車上有兩紙箱，警員隨即將她送往灣仔警署作進一步了解，暫列流浪婦人。<br />\n<br />\n有網民之前拍攝到婦人的蹤影，只見她推着手推車，沿灣仔告士打道中線前行，當時巴士、私家車和的士在她兩旁駛過，但她也毫不理會，及後進入紅隧管道，沿慢線的邊旁前行，旁若無人。<br />\n<br />\n徒步闖紅隧事件並非首次，根據法例，任何人未經批准擅自徒步闖入隧道區，可判罰款5,000元及監禁六個月。<br />\n<br />\n2017年7月 一名內地男遊客，在灣仔買醉後誤闖入紅隧，並步行往九龍，由隧道職員截獲載至紅磡收費廣場，被警員口頭警告後放行。<br />\n2016年6月 一名女子從九龍徒步進入紅隧北面收費廣場，入管道前被隧道職員截停。<br />\n2015年6月 一名女子情緒激動走到紅隧往九龍入口，由隧道職員截停制止，事後送院檢驗。<br />\n2015年3月 一名外籍男子疑醉酒闖入紅隧往九龍方向的管道內，隧道職員發現將他載至紅磡收費廣場，警方到場通知其家人將他接走。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180209/large/1518146818_09a6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180209%2Flarge%2F1518146818_09a6.jpg&h=ac3a6254&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180209/large/1518147469_6116.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180209%2Flarge%2F1518147469_6116.jpg&h=76cce2a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180209/large/1518147470_6b20.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180209%2Flarge%2F1518147470_6b20.jpg&h=c1970132&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180209/large/1518147471_704a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180209%2Flarge%2F1518147471_704a.jpg&h=8af8dbd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180209/57811151\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180209%2F57811151&d=eQrYsoQoGid1d1Qk%2BO0XO9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=62584584\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180209%2F57811151&h=597bde2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180209/57811151</a>"},{"pid":"7d02f83efbbde60beee8c79e5203e21964914a3b","tid":554934,"uid":82382,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T03:43:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd75c7eef83176816260e8b7256b95151c9db08f","tid":554934,"uid":24730,"like":34,"dislike":3,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T03:43:56.000Z","msg":"個樣一睇就知係蝗"},{"pid":"22717775d04a36e28281747e70586dc3d1f4c3c3","tid":554934,"uid":102096,"like":35,"dislike":2,"score":33,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T03:45:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0cd180dfc46640d0adc9a6ce7a998ee49c152d9f","tid":554934,"uid":38456,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T03:47:35.000Z","msg":"我都覺 應該開比行人"},{"pid":"9387bc8166d5443a2d0eed291be1581c6e97d4ad","tid":554934,"uid":117821,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T03:48:45.000Z","msg":"一睇到個post名 已經講左句 痴撚線 條友個腦係咪生係屎忽到？"},{"pid":"3ee96e733309f9ca6e908990504698fd84b0be5e","tid":554934,"uid":8717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9387bc8166d5443a2d0eed291